OL,6,FCompanies are advertising vacancies
OL,7,Fthat pay below the minimum wage on
OL,8,Fonline jobs boards, according to
OL,9,Fresearch by the TUC.
OL,11,FThe union organisation said it found
OL,12,F46 full-time jobs posted on three
OL,13,Fseparate job sites ` Reed, Indeed and
OL,14,FCV-Library ` in a single day in July
OL,15,Fwhich appeared to pay less than the
OL,16,Fnational living wage.
