OL,6,FFor workers between 18 and 20 years
OL,7,Fold, the minimum wage is #8.60 per
OL,8,Fhour.
OL,10,FWhile workers aged under 21 can
OL,11,Ftherefore be paid lower rates of the
OL,12,Fminimum wage, advertising roles at
OL,13,Flower rates potentially excludes older
OL,14,Fworkers and could be unlawful due to
OL,15,Findirect discrimination, the TUC said.
OL,17,FThe research included one advert,
OL,18,Fseeking a graduate copywriter in
OL,19,FHampshire, which gave an annual salary
OL,20,Frange from #15,000 ` #20,000.
